# React

- Function components + hooks only; one component per file, typed props.
- No unnecessary `useEffect` — compute during render or in event handlers.
- Derive state; keep a single source of truth. Stable list `key`s (not index).
- Handle loading / empty / error states explicitly for async data.
- Accessibility required: semantic HTML, labels, keyboard support, focus.
- Push side effects/business logic into hooks or plain modules.
- Memoize only to fix a measured performance problem.
